title: The Artie Quitter Podcast JUN 22 2015 Mon.mp3
description:
After quitting the "Howard Stern Show," surviving a suicide attempt and hosting his own DirecTV program, comedian Artie Lange is venturing into a new frontier -- podcasting.

The show, which sometimes features comedians Joe Matarese, Gino Bisconti, Sue Costello  and Chris Cotton, has the vibe of hanging out with the guys -- talkin' sports and bustin' chops.

Artie,  Gino Bisconti and Chris Cotton are joined on the phone by sports writer, reporter Chris Mannix
